org.grouplens.lenskit.eval

Class ExecutionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.lenskit.eval.ExecutionInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Shareable
public class ExecutionInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable

    Bean containing information about a data set. Used to provide that information to the algorithmInfo, if it needs it for some reason. It is best avoided, but can be useful in certain experimental setups. The evaluators inject it into the configuration, so it is available via DI.

    Since:
    1.1
